# Input

```html
<img
  src="test.png"
  alt="test" />
<br />
<input
  type="text"
  name="test" />
<hr>

```


# Options

```json
{
  "html": {
    "formatter": {
      "bracketSameLine": true
    }
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```html
<img src="test.png" alt="test">
<br>
<input type="text" name="test">
<hr>

```
